Description: Orchestrates RayCloudTools and TreeTools through Docker and
    provides R-native parsers and analysis helpers for RayExtract treefiles,
    including tree smoothing, treeinfo integration, QSM-like conversion,
    volume calculation, center-of-gravity estimation, tree metrics,
    CSV export, and simple plotting helpers.
